snippet.title: AI War 2: "Midnight" Piano Track
snippet.description:
AI War 2 kickstarter is live now!  https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/arcengames/ai-war-ii-0

Pablo is getting pumped for the new project, same as the rest of us -- the core campaign has secured its funding, and we're closing in on reaching the stretch goal that includes new music from him as well as reorchestrations/rearrangements of "top hits" tracks from the original game (and its six expansions).

"Midnight" has always been both a fan favorite as well as a favorite here at Arcen, and Pablo did a quick video showcasing a piano performance of it over the weekend.  Enjoy!
